    <h2 style="color: white; margin-bottom: 2rem; font-size: 2rem; text-align: center; background: linear-gradient(135deg, white, var(--primary)); -webkit-background-clip: text; background-clip: text; color: transparent; font-weight: 700;">Text to Speech: Tips & FAQ</h2>
    
    <div style="display: grid; gap: 2rem; text-align: left;">
