            <h4 style="color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-size: 1.2rem;">How do I get the best AI voice?</h4>
            <p style="color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.6;">For the most natural results, use appropriate punctuation. Commas create brief pauses, while periods create longer ones. You can also try phonetic spelling if the AI is mispronouncing a specific word or brand name.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
