            <p style="color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.6;">Currently, Webtigo supports English (US, UK, AU), French, Spanish, and German. We are constantly updating our model to include more regional accents and languages based on user demand.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
            <h4 style="color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-size: 1.2rem;">Commercial usage limits</h4>
            <p style="color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.6;">The Webtigo free tier allows you to generate speech for personal and educational use. For unlimited high-volume commercial usage, please reach out to us via the contact page or check out the premium dashboard.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div style="margin-top: 3rem; padding: 2.5rem; background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.05); border-radius: 20px; border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2); text-align: center;">
        <h3 style="color: white; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Mastering AI Voices</h3>
        <p style="color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Learn the hidden punctuation tricks that make AI sound human in our deep-dive blog guide.</p>
        <a href="/blog/tts" class="primary-btn" style="text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; width: auto; padding: 0.75rem 2rem;">Read TTS Masterclass</a>
    </div>
</section>